 with CYP450 3A4 inhibitors, particularly potent and moderate inhibitors (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/41073/', '', 'Ulipristal, Danazol, Ospemifene, Raloxifene, Bazedoxifene, Prasterone', '', 1767369485);
